Every document in Atlas will begin with a standard metadata block.

Example:

---
id: STRAT-0017
title: Covered Premium Strategy
type: Strategy
status: Paper
version: 1.3.0
author: Atlas
created: 2026-07-05
updated: 2026-07-05
evidence: B
regime:
  - Bull
  - Neutral
tags:
  - income
  - options
  - premium
relationships:
  created_from:
  validated_by:
  superseded_by:
---

This allows Claude Code to index every document deterministically without parsing prose.
